-- Twitter Picks Berlin For German Headquarters, Focus Says
-- B y   N a o m i   K r e s g e
-- 2012-03-25T12:56:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-25/twitter-picks-berlin-for-german-headquarters-focus-says.html
Twitter Inc. will have its German
headquarters in Berlin,  Focus  magazine reported, citing
unidentified people.  The micro-blogging service picked the German capital over
Hamburg and Munich, the two cities where  Google Inc. (GOOG) ,  Facebook
Inc. (FB) ,  Amazon.com Inc. (AMZN)  and  Microsoft Corp. (MSFT)  have their local
headquarters, the magazine said in an e-mailed preview of an
article.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Naomi Kresge in Berlin at 
 nkresge@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Phil Serafino at 
 pserafino@bloomberg.net  